{"tid":1987004,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（窮L）是日午餐加下午茶（可能連晚餐）","createTime":"2020-04-24T07:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T10:20:08.000Z","uid":256215,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"136bedb1ccf32a8141be8cae4196409ebb13a9bb","tid":1987004,"uid":256215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T07:53:26.000Z","msg":"之前聽有巴打話烏冬要買急凍先好食所以試下。<br />\n<br />\n配前晚食剩既炆牛腩（急凍），紅蘿蔔同 冬菇， 煎蛋同半條青瓜（青瓜佳寶6蚊3條）。<br />\n<br />\n湯用湯粉（ 好耐之前淨落嚟，咪浪費，連跟邊個牌子都唔記得）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LDBkWTX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDBkWTX.jpg&h=1ede7412&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22476dc2652b251120e7e1fe868a2f2c43627e6d","tid":1987004,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T10:20:08.000Z","msg":"都幾好食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}